(Corrects first paragraph to say case instead of lawsuit.)  Brazil ’s federal justice decided
that a federal court in the city of Rio de Janeiro has
jurisdiction to judge a criminal case against Chevron Corp. for
an oil spill off the state’s coast, according to an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
